Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.96,0:00:05.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我 狮堂光与小海、小风三人
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.96,0:00:09.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再度被召唤到异世界锡菲罗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.76,0:00:14.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个国家现在失去 世界的支柱艾美诺公主
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.17,0:00:16.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,面临消灭的危机
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.67,0:00:19.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,攻打这里的奇杰达
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.67,0:00:21.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,决定放弃进攻锡菲罗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.64,0:00:25.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,法连的飞鸟公主 也放弃要当支柱的想法
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.81,0:00:28.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家知道这件事 都由衷地高兴
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.12,0:00:30.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.18,0:00:32.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,新星又出现在城内
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.35,0:00:35.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把兰迪斯带到某个地方
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.66,0:00:40.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果能成为支柱的人是你的话 怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.13,0:00:47.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后我从古列夫那里 知道了新星的真面目
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.43,0:00:51.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原来新星 是我的心所造出来的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.11,0:00:54.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小光…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.98,0:02:36.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第46话 小光大受冲击！新星的真面目
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.05,0:03:42.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,炎之箭
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.30,0:03:53.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,兰迪斯…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.93,0:03:54.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小光
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.37,0:03:58.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,古列夫 兰迪斯他…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.20,0:04:01.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也在追踪兰迪斯的意识
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.84,0:04:03.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是找不到位置
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.61,0:04:05.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,兰迪斯受伤了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.88,0:04:08.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,流了好多血
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.61,0:04:10.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,新星把他…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.58,0:04:12.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,冷静下来 小光
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.42,0:04:16.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的心乱掉的话 新星会变得更强的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.86,0:04:22.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我确实听到某种爆炸的声音
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.86,0:04:24.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,发生什么事呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.66,0:04:26.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,飞鸟公主没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.50,0:04:29.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小风 你也有听到吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.03,0:04:33.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的心听到小光的惨叫声
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.20,0:04:36.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小光好像在哭的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.68,0:04:47.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家退后
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.68,0:04:53.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,水之龙
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.90,0:05:00.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,伤口又愈合了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.44,0:05:13.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,碧岚疾风
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.19,0:05:24.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在上方
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.23,0:05:34.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,菲力欧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.24,0:05:47.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,飞鸟公主
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.24,0:06:15.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,苍暴龙卷
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.98,0:06:21.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不能在这里输掉
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.31,0:06:23.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好不容易和大家取得共识
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.00,0:06:44.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,泰塔 泰多娜
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.51,0:06:49.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,危险
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.68,0:06:54.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,菲力欧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.18,0:07:00.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为了保护最喜欢的人们
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.68,0:07:02.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们才选择了战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.69,0:07:05.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,绝对…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.46,0:07:06.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不能输
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.80,0:07:19.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,碧岚旋风
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.81,0:07:31.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,冰之刃
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.72,0:07:41.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,成功了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.43,0:07:46.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,打赢了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.43,0:07:48.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了 飞鸟公主
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.90,0:07:50.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小风果然厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.94,0:07:54.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小海 你会新魔法了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.90,0:07:56.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你也是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.44,0:08:01.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不！！不！！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.75,0:08:04.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小光
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.08,0:08:06.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了？小光
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.78,0:08:08.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不可能…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.62,0:08:11.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不可能…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.36,0:08:17.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,叫做新星的少女
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.69,0:08:19.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是你的影子
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.37,0:08:35.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那时候我一直在心中呐喊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.71,0:08:37.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不应该这样
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.72,0:08:40.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不应该这样的！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.06,0:08:51.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是我说不出口
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.23,0:08:52.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为如果说出来
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.73,0:08:55.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的心可能会碎掉
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.23,0:08:59.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小海 小风一定也是同样的感受
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.74,0:09:05.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾美诺公主 好不容易获得自由的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.58,0:09:14.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以我才说不出口
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.25,0:09:17.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对 你说不出口的心灵呐喊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.82,0:09:19.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,化成强烈光芒
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.69,0:09:22.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在锡菲罗留下了影子
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.86,0:09:24.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就是新星
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.86,0:09:27.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没错 新星是你的影子
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.03,0:09:30.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的心灵的一部份
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.34,0:09:38.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,后悔 悲伤与对自己内心的焦虑
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.51,0:09:40.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这一切
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.18,0:09:43.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在那瞬间徘徊在锡菲罗 留了下来
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.91,0:09:46.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我在那时候
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.72,0:09:48.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对自己…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.08,0:09:51.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对必需跟艾美诺公主为敌的自己
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.19,0:09:53.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知道该怎么处置
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.69,0:09:56.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为小光讨厌自己
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.36,0:09:59.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以我最喜欢小光了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.53,0:10:05.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以新星才说喜欢我
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.90,0:10:07.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为我…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.07,0:10:10.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那时候我无法原谅自己
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.64,0:10:11.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小光
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.21,0:10:16.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,新星是我的心
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.71,0:10:19.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么 让兰迪斯受伤的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.02,0:10:21.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是我？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.57,0:10:42.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了 新星
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.17,0:10:47.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的心…在痛
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.68,0:10:54.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大概是那个魔法骑士的心 影响到你了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.75,0:11:00.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,新星抓来的这个男人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.02,0:11:04.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,心志强到吓人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.19,0:11:10.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的坚强 将被用来帮助我
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.14,0:11:20.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小光在哭
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.38,0:11:23.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想着兰迪斯而哭
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.71,0:11:25.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奇怪了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.38,0:11:26.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的胸口好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.15,0:11:29.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.20,0:11:59.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小光
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.50,0:12:03.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你受伤了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.77,0:12:07.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小光…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.84,0:12:10.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.11,0:12:12.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,兰迪斯…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.38,0:12:16.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为我而受伤
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.68,0:12:18.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为我…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.22,0:12:19.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被掳走了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.48,0:12:22.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被掳走？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.02,0:12:24.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被谁？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.32,0:12:26.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被我…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.49,0:12:32.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,导师古列夫
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.03,0:12:33.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,您的身体这样…太勉强了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.40,0:12:35.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,勉强也行
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.20,0:12:37.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,导师！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.70,0:12:40.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以我的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.70,0:12:43.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想找出迪波尼亚的位置
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.54,0:12:50.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但只能够查到 她在锡菲罗的附近
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.71,0:12:55.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,知道的人只有爱尔希欧蕾
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.22,0:12:56.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.22,0:12:57.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不快问出来的话
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.72,0:12:59.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.22,0:13:05.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又会让异世界的少女们伤心
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.23,0:13:14.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个少女是小光的心
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.07,0:13:19.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听说你是兰迪斯的朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.74,0:13:22.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以我向你道歉
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.38,0:13:26.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么来找我
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.58,0:13:31.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是进攻锡菲罗的 欧多札姆的司令哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.09,0:13:35.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你为什么要独自过来？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.09,0:13:39.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想要对 兰迪斯喜欢的人道歉
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.93,0:13:46.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,伊格尔你其实…也喜欢兰迪斯的…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.27,0:13:48.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.77,0:13:53.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在我若抱住你
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.11,0:13:56.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知会不会 被喜爱你的人们责骂
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.13,0:14:10.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.79,0:14:12.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也知道你是敌人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.96,0:14:17.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但不知道为什么 就是没办法讨厌你
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.23,0:14:20.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在战舰里面 你对我很好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.30,0:14:23.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在与新星的战斗中 你也救过兰迪斯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.81,0:14:26.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这些我都无法忘记
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.08,0:14:29.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也一样哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.25,0:14:36.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,导师古列夫
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.39,0:14:38.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,普蕾西雅
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.11,0:14:59.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,兰迪斯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.41,0:15:04.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在保护我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.78,0:15:09.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是因为我太可爱了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.42,0:15:15.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小光姐姐她们不要紧吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.86,0:15:17.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有受伤吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.29,0:15:21.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没问题的 姐姐她们很强的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.70,0:15:26.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们若能变得像姐姐那么强就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.45,0:15:38.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,卡尔汀娜
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.59,0:15:43.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么？发生什么事了？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.99,0:15:50.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,锡菲罗的崩溃加速了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.06,0:15:54.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小海
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.83,0:15:56.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿斯克特
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.07,0:15:59.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.64,0:16:01.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不太好说出口 但小海她…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.64,0:16:04.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.34,0:16:09.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我喜欢小海
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.18,0:16:11.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是我真实的心意
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.42,0:16:16.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算小海 不把我当成特殊的人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.02,0:16:22.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我还是喜欢小海 这样我就很幸福、很满足了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.26,0:16:25.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿斯克特
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.20,0:16:28.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要到小海她们身边去
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.87,0:16:32.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好 你就充满干劲地去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.20,0:16:37.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿斯克特长大了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.57,0:16:40.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真不知道该感到高兴还是寂寞
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.78,0:16:42.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的心情好复杂
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.25,0:16:46.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要哭
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.08,0:16:51.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你哭 会令兰迪斯伤心的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.42,0:16:56.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,兰迪斯一定讨厌
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.93,0:16:59.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我杀死了兰迪斯的哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.63,0:17:02.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道他不可能喜欢我
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.43,0:17:04.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但我就是喜欢他
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.10,0:17:06.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,自己也不知道为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.27,0:17:08.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.11,0:17:16.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能够找出理由的喜欢 就不是真的喜欢了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.81,0:17:21.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然不知道为什么 总之你喜欢他吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.25,0:17:30.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,前任支柱艾美诺公主 一定想着跟你一样的问题
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.16,0:17:35.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,身为支柱的自己 为什么会爱上人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.17,0:17:39.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么无法阻止自己的心
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.10,0:17:44.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想 她一定也找不出答案
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.84,0:17:49.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,即使如此 她还是喜欢上谢加图
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.85,0:17:55.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,每个人都有 自己无法控制的感情的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.32,0:18:00.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总是为那失控的心而烦恼
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.62,0:18:06.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也是 可能的话 想跟你这个敌人当朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.03,0:18:09.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对兰迪斯也是？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.17,0:18:11.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.87,0:18:14.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我确实爱欧多札姆
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.84,0:18:17.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不想让那个国家灭亡
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.04,0:18:18.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.51,0:18:19.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.68,0:18:21.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我真正的愿望
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.88,0:18:23.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,却怎样都抹灭不掉
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.35,0:18:26.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真正的愿望？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.19,0:18:33.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,伊格尔 你怎么了 伊格尔
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.23,0:18:38.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,伊格尔
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.53,0:18:42.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别在意
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.37,0:18:44.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过 说恐怕是白说吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.54,0:18:46.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,伊格尔
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.54,0:18:55.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,告诉我 爱尔希欧蕾
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.05,0:18:57.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,控制你的迪波尼亚在哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.88,0:19:03.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢加图的弟弟 兰迪斯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.55,0:19:06.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被抓去迪波尼亚那里了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.39,0:19:08.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,得赶快把他救出来
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.39,0:19:12.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢加图大人的弟弟？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.76,0:19:17.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样下去锡菲罗真的会崩溃
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.40,0:19:20.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,告诉我 爱尔希欧蕾
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.20,0:19:24.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有谢加图大人的锡菲罗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.54,0:19:26.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,变成怎样我都不在乎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.58,0:19:34.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,使我不惜背叛导师 抛弃一切的人 已不在人世
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.59,0:19:41.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么我会活下来呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.39,0:19:45.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算他不爱我
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.73,0:19:49.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,至少让我跟他一起死啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.23,0:19:52.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爱尔希欧蕾
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.78,0:20:02.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,伊格尔 你生病了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.71,0:20:04.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,兰迪斯知道吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.08,0:20:10.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,唯有兰迪斯 我不希望他知道
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.32,0:20:16.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的时间所剩不多
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.73,0:20:21.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你或我…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.10,0:20:24.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能成为支柱的人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.00,0:20:25.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是我们之中一人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.17,0:20:30.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把这件事弄清楚吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.84,0:20:36.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不能让欧多札姆就此灭亡
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.85,0:20:42.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但你也不愿意 锡菲罗就此崩溃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.62,0:20:50.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果 我有当支柱的资格
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.16,0:20:52.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要留在锡菲罗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.50,0:20:56.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,身为支柱 让世界不致于崩溃
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.17,0:20:58.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,相对的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.67,0:21:03.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要让欧多札姆的人 进入这个国家
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.77,0:21:05.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,了解支柱系统的秘密
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.38,0:21:09.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且 不让他们做出任何侵略的行为
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.65,0:21:11.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我保证
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.99,0:21:19.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后 如果…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.52,0:21:21.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是支柱的话
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.20,0:21:26.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.83,0:21:29.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,打算如何处理这个国家？
